-12-11T08:55:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>棍波拎左學牌<br />\n學左兩個鐘<br />\n有1個多鐘都係馬路行<br />\n然後學上斜 <br />\n最難係泊車<br />\n成個學車都唔記得死左幾次火<br />\n唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有邊個學車冇死火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n泊位果啲驚唔記得，可以上完堂寫notes 或者上youtube 睇下教學:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/BpkSlHgXiLE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FBpkSlHgXiLE&d=6zjhOazpj6N4jXPNlI5NiTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=4353bb14\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/BpkSlHgXiLE</a></blockquote><br />\n我真係冇死過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但就開頭每次起步都慢過龜比人屌"},{"pid":"1b8316ae46f57ea740a266830c927c2d4786c743","tid":495762,"uid":3647,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T08:55:43.000Z","msg":"壓力 係黎自車軚"},{"pid":"da44e1f8ca10c438d0f4bb44f69320a73086ec4e","tid":495762,"uid":81852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T08:55:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dcdabca69650571595f74da2769f56c757158ad5","tid":495762,"uid":52215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T08:56:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第一堂兩個鐘<br />\n下堂已經唔想再去<br />\n教我個個仲要係親戚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n親戚教咪幾好<br />\n唔會一二一二咁小你啦最起碼"},{"pid":"1a405528851ea154eeca929d83129ab5b44a8b87","tid":495762,"uid":58699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T08:59:07.000Z","msg":"正常架 揸耐啲會享受"},{"pid":"8308199e387e5c8e5dfe767254fb88ac433b2396","tid":495762,"uid":8572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T09:00:48.000Z","msg":"有幾難 死火因爲你唔聽書姐  慢慢黎 停就一定要踩低極力子"},{"pid":"b1f99fd0adf2d350eae67132644529012570c568","tid":495762,"uid":45290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T09:00:48.000Z","msg":"親戚教咁好<br />\n有冇收你平啲?"},{"pid":"55884609375f27360633ba5e9c3da84e5b246965","tid"